# Ingestion Engine Optimization (V5.2.34)

Speed up the statement parsing process and remove legacy code bloat from [ledger.core.js](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/ledger.core.js) and [app.js](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/app.js).

## Proposed Changes

### [ledger.core.js](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/ledger.core.js)

#### 1. Centralized Parser Engine [OPTIMIZE]
- Move all regex patterns (RBC, Mastercard, Brands, Cleaning prefixes) to a top-level `PARSERS` object within the IIFE.
- Pre-compile all regexes to avoid re-compilation during loops.

#### 2. Legacy Bloat Removal [CLEANUP]
- Prune the [load()](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/ledger.core.js#118-155) function of the "Legacy Repair Phase" (2026->2023 repair and cleanDescription backfill).
- Remove redundant console logs and commented-out code segments.

#### 3. Streamlined Intelligence [OPTIMIZE]
- Optimize [detectInstitution](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/ledger.core.js#433-498) to use a more efficient matching strategy.
- Batch the description cleaning logic in `Brain.cleanDescription` to reduce string allocations.

#### 4. Hardened Polarity Detection [CLEANUP]
- Refactor the signage logic in [processUpload](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/ledger.core.js#499-610) to be more declarative using a mapping or helper function.

### [app.js](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/app.js)

#### 1. Minimalist UI Refinement [AESTHETIC]
- **One-Line Metadata**: Refactor the ATI Metadata line to be minimal, removing labels like "BRAND:" and "CARD#:" in favor of a clean "MASTERCARD • XXXX-XXXX" format.
- **One-Line Descriptions**: Revert the description column to a high-fidelity single line. Move the raw trace to a subtle tooltip or remove it if not needed for the professional view.
- **Consise Headers**: Ensure all grid headers are short and professional (e.g., "Ref", "Date", "Payee", "Amount", "Balance").

#### 2. UI Performance [OPTIMIZE]
- Ensure [render()](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/app.js#39-44) is only called when state actually changes during ingestion.
- Batch grid updates if multiple files are uploaded.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run existing ingestion tests to ensure no regression in parsing accuracy.
- Benchmark parsing speed with large PDF statements (100+ transactions).

### Manual Verification
- Upload the Mastercard statement and verify:
    - Ingestion speed is noticeably faster (check console timestamps).
    - UI is "Minimalist & Professional": one-line text, no clutter.
    - All forensic alignments (Dates, Card#, Payees) remain 100% correct.
    - No "Legacy Repair" logs appear in the console.
